cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper deals with neural networks and their optimization, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the performance of the network in image classification tasks (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper proposes a new method for approximating the tangent subspace, which is a common technique in optimization algorithms (cs.AI).
